### ================== RUTAS CON AUTENTICACIÓN ==================

### Obtener todos los propietarios (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/owners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obtener propietario por ID (CON token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/owners/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear un nuevo propietario (CON token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/owners
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Gómez",
  "phone": "3009876543",
  "email": "ana.gomez@example.com",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Actualizar un propietario (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/owners/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ana Gómez Actualizada",
  "phone": "3001239876",
  "email": "ana.updated@example.com",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar un propietario físicamente (CON token)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/owners/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Desactivar un propietario (CON token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/owners/1/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
